<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN312-intro">tiṇai, vākai; tuṟai, mūtiṉmullai. poṉmuṭiyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN312">
<l>īṉṟupuṟan taruta leṉṟalaik kaṭaṉē</l>
<l>cāṉṟō ṉākkuta ṟantaikkuk kaṭaṉē</l>
<l>vēlvaṭittuk koṭuttal kollaṟkuk kaṭaṉē</l>
<l>naṉṉaṭai nalkal vēntaṟkuk kaṭaṉē</l>
<l>yoḷiṟuvā ḷaruñcama murukkik</l>
<l>kaḷiṟeṟintu peyartal kāḷaikkuk kaṭaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bringing forth [and] protecting [children] is the duty upon me. </l>
<l>Making [them] into worthy men is the father’s duty.</l>
<l>Forming spears [and] giving [them] is the smith’s duty.</l>
<l>Granting [gifts for] good conduct is the king’s duty.</l>
<l>Crushing [enemies] in difficult battle with shining swords</l>
<l>[and] coming back after attacking elephant bulls is the young man’s duty.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
